---

<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32">
  <div class="animate-fade-up">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
      <span class="inline-block w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 pulse-dot"></span>
      <span class="text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">Based in Ottawa, Canada</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h1
    class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 tracking-tight leading-[1.1] animate-fade-up animate-delay-1"
  >
    I'm Tom &mdash;<br />
    <span class="gradient-text">economist</span> turned <span class="gradient-text">builder</span>.
  </h1>

  <p
    class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-surface-600 dark:text-surface-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed animate-fade-up animate-delay-2"
  >
    By day I crunch national-level data at the Privy Council Office.
    By night I build the apps I wish existed. I believe the best way
    to understand a problem is to build the solution.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-fade-up animate-delay-3">
    <a
      href="/projects"
      class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-surface-900 dark:bg-surface-100 text-surface-50 dark:text-surface-900 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-surface-700 dark:hover:bg-surface-300 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]"
    >
      See what I've built
      <svg
        class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke="currentColor"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/blog"
      class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-surface-300 dark:border-surface-700 text-surface-700 dark:text-surface-300 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-surface-100 dark:hover:bg-surface-800 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]"
    >
      Read my writing
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Currently section -->
  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-surface-200 dark:border-surface-800 animate-fade-up animate-delay-4">
    <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-surface-400 dark:text-surface-500 mb-4">Currently</p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
      <div>
        <p class="text-surface-400 dark:text-surface-500">Working on</p>
        <p class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-200 font-medium">HangulGogo</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-surface-400 dark:text-surface-500">Day job</p>
        <p class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-200 font-medium">Privy Council Office</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-surface-400 dark:text-surface-500">Playing</p>
        <p class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-200 font-medium">Badminton</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
